These crispy fish burgers are the best treats to serve at a games night with your friends or a dinner party with your loved ones.  Throw some oven-baked fries into the oven and serve them with these yummy burgers for a filling and wholesome meal.  This recipe comes with a delicious lemon garlic mayo sauce which you can make more of and enjoy with your potato fries.    For the burgers  For the lemon garlic mayo  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Creamy chicken lasagna This recipe was found on kitchensanctuary.com